#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Buddhavagga"
msgstr "1. The Buddhas"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Vipassīsutta"
msgstr "4. About Vipassī"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati … pe …"
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.4:1.2"
msgid ""
"“vipassissa, bhikkhave, bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa pubbeva sambodhā "
"anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, Vipassī the Blessed One, the perfected one, the fully awakened "
"Buddha had this thought before his awakening, when he was still unawakened "
"but intent on awakening:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘kicchaṃ vatāyaṃ loko āpanno jāyati ca jīyati ca mīyati ca cavati ca "
"upapajjati ca."
msgstr ""
"‘Alas, this world has fallen into trouble. It’s born, grows old, dies, "
"passes away, and is reborn,"

msgctxt "sn12.4:1.4"
msgid "Atha ca panimassa dukkhassa nissaraṇaṃ nappajānāti jarāmaraṇassa."
msgstr ""
"yet it doesn’t understand how to escape from this suffering, from old age "
"and death."

msgctxt "sn12.4:1.5"
msgid "Kudāssu nāma imassa dukkhassa nissaraṇaṃ paññāyissati jarāmaraṇassā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, when will an escape be found from this suffering, from old age and "
"death?’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī, the one intent on awakening, thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:2.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati jarāmaraṇaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what exists is there old age and death? What is a condition for old "
"age and death?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:2.4"
msgid "‘jātiyā kho sati jarāmaraṇaṃ hoti, jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When rebirth exists there’s old age and death. Rebirth is a condition for "
"old age and death.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:3.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati jāti hoti, kiṃpaccayā jātī’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists is there rebirth? What is a condition for rebirth?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:3.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:3.4"
msgid "‘bhave kho sati jāti hoti, bhavapaccayā jātī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When continued existence exists there’s rebirth. Continued existence is a "
"condition for rebirth.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:4.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati bhavo hoti, kiṃpaccayā bhavo’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what exists is there continued existence? What is a condition for "
"continued existence?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:4.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:4.4"
msgid "‘upādāne kho sati bhavo hoti, upādānapaccayā bhavo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When grasping exists there’s continued existence. Grasping is a condition "
"for continued existence.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:5.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati upādānaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā upādānan’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists is there grasping? What is a condition for grasping?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:5.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:5.4"
msgid "‘taṇhāya kho sati upādānaṃ hoti, taṇhāpaccayā upādānan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When craving exists there’s grasping. Craving is a condition for grasping.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:6.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati taṇhā hoti, kiṃpaccayā taṇhā’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists is there craving? What is a condition for craving?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:6.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:6.4"
msgid "‘vedanāya kho sati taṇhā hoti, vedanāpaccayā taṇhā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When feeling exists there’s craving. Feeling is a condition for craving.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:7.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati vedanā hoti, kiṃpaccayā vedanā’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists is there feeling? What is a condition for feeling?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:7.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:7.4"
msgid "‘phasse kho sati vedanā hoti, phassapaccayā vedanā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When contact exists there’s feeling. Contact is a condition for feeling.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:8.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:8.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati phasso hoti, kiṃpaccayā phasso’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists is there contact? What is a condition for contact?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:8.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:8.4"
msgid "‘saḷāyatane kho sati phasso hoti, saḷāyatanapaccayā phasso’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When the six sense fields exist there’s contact. The six sense fields are a "
"condition for contact.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:9.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:9.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati saḷāyatanaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā saḷāyatanan’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what exists are there the six sense fields? What is a condition for "
"the six sense fields?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:9.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:9.4"
msgid "‘nāmarūpe kho sati saḷāyatanaṃ hoti, nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatanan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When name and form exist there’s the six sense fields. Name and form are a "
"condition for the six sense fields.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:10.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:10.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati nāmarūpaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā nāmarūpan’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what exists are there name and form? What is a condition for name and "
"form?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:10.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:10.4"
msgid "‘viññāṇe kho sati nāmarūpaṃ hoti, viññāṇapaccayā nāmarūpan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When consciousness exists there are name and form. Consciousness is a "
"condition for name and form.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:11.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:11.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati viññāṇaṃ hoti, kiṃpaccayā viññāṇan’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what exists is there consciousness? What is a condition for "
"consciousness?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:11.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:11.4"
msgid "‘saṅkhāresu kho sati viññāṇaṃ hoti, saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When choices exist there’s consciousness. Choices are a condition for "
"consciousness.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:12.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:12.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho sati saṅkhārā honti, kiṃpaccayā saṅkhārā’ti?"
msgstr "‘When what exists are there choices? What is a condition for choices?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:12.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:12.4"
msgid "‘avijjāya kho sati saṅkhārā honti, avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When ignorance exists there are choices. Ignorance is a condition for "
"choices.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:13.1"
msgid "Iti hidaṃ avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "And so, ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.4:13.2"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.4:13.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.4:13.4"
msgid ""
"‘Samudayo, samudayo’ti kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa pubbe "
"ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā "
"udapādi, āloko udapādi."
msgstr ""
"‘Origination, origination.’ While Vipassī was intent on awakening, such was "
"the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, and light that arose in him "
"regarding teachings not learned before from another."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:14.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘kimhi nu kho asati jarāmaraṇaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no old age and death? When what ceases do "
"old age and death cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:14.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:14.4"
msgid ""
"‘jātiyā kho asati jarāmaraṇaṃ na hoti, jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When rebirth doesn’t exist there’s no old age and death. When rebirth "
"ceases, old age and death cease.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:15.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:15.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati jāti na hoti, kissa nirodhā jātinirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no rebirth? When what ceases does rebirth "
"cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:15.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:15.4"
msgid "‘bhave kho asati jāti na hoti, bhavanirodhā jātinirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When continued existence doesn’t exist there’s no rebirth. When continued "
"existence ceases, rebirth ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:16.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:16.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati bhavo na hoti, kissa nirodhā bhavanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no continued existence? When what ceases "
"does continued existence cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:16.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:16.4"
msgid "‘upādāne kho asati bhavo na hoti, upādānanirodhā bhavanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When grasping doesn’t exist there’s no continued existence. When grasping "
"ceases, continued existence ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:17.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:17.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati upādānaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā upādānanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no grasping? When what ceases does "
"grasping cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:17.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:17.4"
msgid "‘taṇhāya kho asati upādānaṃ na hoti, taṇhānirodhā upādānanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When craving doesn’t exist there’s no grasping. When craving ceases, "
"grasping ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:18.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:18.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati taṇhā na hoti, kissa nirodhā taṇhānirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no craving? When what ceases does craving "
"cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:18.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:18.4"
msgid "‘vedanāya kho asati taṇhā na hoti, vedanānirodhā taṇhānirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When feeling doesn’t exist there’s no craving. When feeling ceases, craving "
"ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:19.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:19.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati vedanā na hoti, kissa nirodhā vedanānirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no feeling? When what ceases does feeling "
"cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:19.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:19.4"
msgid "‘phasse kho asati vedanā na hoti, phassanirodhā vedanānirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When contact doesn’t exist there’s no feeling. When contact ceases, feeling "
"ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:20.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:20.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati phasso na hoti, kissa nirodhā phassanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no contact? When what ceases does contact "
"cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:20.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:20.4"
msgid ""
"‘saḷāyatane kho asati phasso na hoti, saḷāyatananirodhā phassanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When the six sense fields don’t exist there’s no contact. When the six "
"sense fields cease, contact ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:21.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:21.2"
msgid ""
"‘kimhi nu kho asati saḷāyatanaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā saḷāyatananirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist are there no six sense fields? When what ceases do "
"the six sense fields cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:21.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:21.4"
msgid ""
"‘nāmarūpe kho asati saḷāyatanaṃ na hoti, nāmarūpanirodhā "
"saḷāyatananirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When name and form don’t exist there are no six sense fields. When name and "
"form cease, the six sense fields cease.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:22.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:22.2"
msgid ""
"‘kimhi nu kho asati nāmarūpaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā nāmarūpanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist are there no name and form? When what ceases do "
"name and form cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:22.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:22.4"
msgid ""
"‘viññāṇe kho asati nāmarūpaṃ na hoti, viññāṇanirodhā nāmarūpanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When consciousness doesn’t exist there are no name and form. When "
"consciousness ceases, name and form cease.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:23.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:23.2"
msgid "‘kimhi nu kho asati viññāṇaṃ na hoti, kissa nirodhā viññāṇanirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist is there no consciousness? When what ceases does "
"consciousness cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:23.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:23.4"
msgid ""
"‘saṅkhāresu kho asati viññāṇaṃ na hoti, saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When choices don’t exist there’s no consciousness. When choices cease, "
"consciousness ceases.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:24.1"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa etadahosi:"
msgstr "Then Vipassī thought:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:24.2"
msgid ""
"‘kimhi nu kho asati saṅkhārā na honti, kissa nirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘When what doesn’t exist are there no choices? When what ceases do choices "
"cease?’"

msgctxt "sn12.4:24.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa yoniso manasikārā ahu paññāya "
"abhisamayo:"
msgstr "Then, through proper attention, Vipassī comprehended with wisdom:"

msgctxt "sn12.4:24.4"
msgid ""
"‘avijjāya kho asati saṅkhārā na honti, avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘When ignorance doesn’t exist there are no choices. When ignorance ceases, "
"choices cease.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:25.1"
msgid "Iti hidaṃ avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr "And so, when ignorance ceases, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.4:25.2"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.4:25.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotīti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases."

msgctxt "sn12.4:25.4"
msgid ""
"‘Nirodho, nirodho’ti kho, bhikkhave, vipassissa bodhisattassa pubbe "
"ananussutesu dhammesu cakkhuṃ udapādi, ñāṇaṃ udapādi, paññā udapādi, vijjā "
"udapādi, āloko udapādī”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Cessation, cessation.’ Such was the vision, knowledge, wisdom, realization, "
"and light that arose in Vipassī, the one intent on awakening, regarding "
"teachings not learned before from another.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.4:25.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.4:26.1"
msgid "(Sattannampi buddhānaṃ evaṃ vitthāretabbo.)"
msgstr ""
"(The text should be expanded in this way for each of the seven Buddhas.)"
